name: Earth Ma
description:
Her fierce Soul burned like the Sun.
She watched over the village with eyes of protection and safety.
The villagers paid tithes with offerings of goats and sheep. She accepted them with an open heart however her truest love was for the honesty of the village. As long as they lived in truth she would always offer a gaze of security. They would never go without.Each resident would be provided with everything they needed.
